00:08:40.680 --> 00:08:42.480
Siento que

00:08:42.920 --> 00:08:44.360
habrá algo interesante en esta boda.

00:09:22.280 --> 00:09:23.440
Nos encontramos de nuevo.

00:09:23.920 --> 00:09:25.520
